### Wait for Page Screenshot Match

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/api/class-pageassertions.md

The toHaveScreenshot method waits for two consecutive page screenshots to yield the same result and then compares the last screenshot with the expectation. This assertion works exclusively with the Playwright test runner. It accepts various options to customize the screenshot comparison.

```js
await expect(page).toHaveScreenshot();
```

