### Configure Screenshot Comparison Tolerance in JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/release-notes-js.md

Shows how to configure fine-grained screenshot comparison using maxDiffPixels option with toMatchSnapshot. This allows specifying the maximum number of different pixels acceptable in a screenshot comparison. The option can be set per test or globally in TestConfig.expect.

```javascript
expect(await page.screenshot()).toMatchSnapshot({
  maxDiffPixels: 27, // allow no more than 27 different pixels.
});
```

